alue="IFRIC 1" class="- topic/data "/><data name="paranum" value="IE8" class="- topic/data "/></prolog><body class="- topic/body "><p id="IFRIC01_P0089" class="- topic/p ">Assume that a market‑based discounted cash flow valuation of CU115,000 is obtained at 31 December 2002. It includes an allowance of CU11,600 for decommissioning costs, which represents no change to the original estimate, after the unwinding of three years’ discount. The amounts included in the statement of financial position at 31 December 2002 are therefore: </p><table outputclass="ruled" id="IFRIC01_TAB0003" base="SL76019" frame="none" orient="port" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colnum="1" colname="C1" colwidth="85*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colnum="2" colname="C2" colwidth="15*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="right" class="- topic/colspec "/><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="C1" class="- topic/entry "> <p id="IFRIC01_P0090" typeface="sansserif" class="- topic/p "/></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right" class="- topic/entry "> <p id="IFRIC01_P0091" typeface="sansserif" class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">CU</b></p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="C1" align="left" class="- topic/entry "> <p typeface="sansserif" id="IFRIC01_P0092" base="F611458" class="- topic/p ">Asset at valuation (1) </p></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right" class="- topic/entry "> <p id="IFRIC01_P0093" typeface="sansserif" class="- topic/p ">126,600</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="C1" align="left" class="- topic/entry "> <p typeface="sansserif" id="IFRIC01_P0094" base="F611477" class="- topic/p ">Accumulated depreciation </p></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right" class="- topic/entry "> <p id="IFRIC01_P0095" typeface="sansserif" class="- topic/p ">nil </p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="C1" align="left" class=