gn="left" class="- topic/entry "> <ol outputclass="static" id="IFRIC01_L0009" base="SL146191" type="decimal" class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><li_value class="+ topic/ph ifrs-d/li_value ">1</li_value> <p id="IFRIC01_P0108" base="SL146193" class="- topic/p ">Valuation obtained of CU115,000 plus decommissioning costs of CU11,600, allowed for in the valuation but recognised as a separate liability = CU126,600. </p></li><li class="- topic/li "><li_value class="+ topic/ph ifrs-d/li_value ">2</li_value> <p id="IFRIC01_P0109" base="SL146195" class="- topic/p ">Three years’ depreciation on original cost CU120,000 × <sup class="+ topic/ph hi-d/sup ">3</sup>/<sub class="+ topic/ph hi-d/sub ">40</sub> = CU9,000  plus cumulative discount on CU10,000 at 5 per cent compound = CU1,600;  total CU10,600.</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><li_value class="+ topic/ph ifrs-d/li_value ">3</li_value> <p id="IFRIC01_P0110" base="SL146197" class="- topic/p ">Revalued amount CU126,600 less previous net book value of CU111,000 (cost CU120,000 less accumulated depreciation CU9,000). </p></li></ol></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></body></paragraph>